{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/independent-water-commission/about","content_id":"112c91cc-50ae-47da-b026-541b723a0776","description":"The Independent Water Commission was established in October 2024.","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Independent Water Commission was established in October 2024 to deliver recommendations to government on reforms to the water sector.</p>\n\n<p>It is chaired by Former Deputy Governor of the Bank of England, Sir Jon Cunliffe.</p>\n\n<p>The Commission is focused on ensuring there is a sufficiently robust and stable regulatory framework to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>attract the investment needed for the future</li>\n  <li>speed up infrastructure delivery</li>\n  <li>restore confidence in the sector</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>As set out in the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/independent-commission-on-the-water-sector-regulatory-system-terms-of-reference\">Terms of Reference</a>, the Commission is operating independently of the UK and Welsh Ministers.</p>\n\n<p>The Chair and advisory group are supported by a Defra Secretariat.</p>\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2025-01-29T10:32:45Z"}],"corporate_information_groups":[],"organisation":"6b974c0e-bcdc-4f4c-ac1c-706711ce21ea","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"about","first_published_at":"2025-01-29T10:32:45+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/independent-water-commission/about","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/independent-water-commission/about","base_path":"/government/organisations/independent-water-commission/about","content_id":"112c91cc-50ae-47da-b026-541b723a0776","document_type":"about","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-01-29T10:32:45Z","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","title":"About us","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/ind